><i class=\"fas fa-bars\"></i></button></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Come convertire HEIC in JPG: guida completa\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-17\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-17\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me\"},\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me/it/blog/how-to-convert-heic-to-jpg\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://toolpic.me/it/blog/how-to-convert-heic-to-jpg\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/it\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/it/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Come convertire HEIC in JPG: guida completa\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/it/blog/how-to-convert-heic-to-jpg\"}]}</script><div class=\"background-grid\"></div><article class=\"max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-24\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300 mb-8\" href=\"/it/blog\"><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-left text-xs\"></i>Blog</a><header class=\"mb-12\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4 gradient-text\">Come convertire HEIC in JPG: guida completa</h1><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt text-xs\"></i>17 marzo 2026</span><span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-clock text-xs\"></i>4 min di lettura</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-12 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/blog/heic-to-jpg-hero.jpg\" alt=\"Come convertire HEIC in JPG: guida completa\" class=\"w-full h-auto\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-10\"><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Cos&#x27;e il formato HEIC e perche l&#x27;iPhone lo utilizza</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">HEIC (High Efficiency Image Container) e stato adottato da Apple come formato fotografico predefinito a partire da iOS 11. 265.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Quando serve convertire HEIC in JPG</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">La situazione piu comune si verifica quando vuoi inviare le tue foto iPhone a qualcuno che usa Windows o Android. Potrebbe avere difficolta ad aprire il file HEIC. Allo stesso modo, molti client email e piattaforme social non visualizzano correttamente i file HEIC.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Consigli per mantenere la qualita nella conversione</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">Nella conversione da HEIC a JPG e importante tenere presente alcuni aspetti. Innanzitutto, JPEG e un formato lossy, quindi una leggera perdita di qualita e inevitabile. Tuttavia, con impostazioni di qualita dell&#x27;85-95%, la differenza e praticamente invisibile a occhio nudo.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Come convertire HEIC in JPG con ToolPic</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">Apri il Convertitore di Immagini di ToolPic e trascina i tuoi file HEIC oppure sfoglia per caricarli. Puoi caricare piu file contemporaneamente per una facile conversione batch.</div></section></div><div class=\"mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-wrench text-[var(--color-purple)]\"></i>Strumenti correlati</h3><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><a class=\"glass-card p-5 block hover:border-[var(--color-border-hover)] transition-all duration-300 group\" href=\"/it/tools/convertitore-immagini\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-exchange-alt text-sm text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h4 class=\"font-semibold group-hover:text-[var(--color-purple)] transition-colors\">Convertitore immagini</h4></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Converti immagini tra formati JPG, PNG, WebP, AVIF, BMP istantaneamente.</p></a></div></div></article><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-[#040405] border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-10 mb-12\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><span class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-white text-base\"></i></span><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">ToolPic</span></div><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-[300px] leading-relaxed\">Strumenti online gratuiti per immagini e video. 100% nel browser, i tuoi file non lasciano mai il tuo dispositivo.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Strumenti</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-30